arStrings.szText: Iâ€™m not certain. I expected death. Not... this.
At this moment, balance is the best we can hope for. Balance with the curse in my own body, balance with the curse in this city.
We must keep the dregs contained. If you find anything unusual in the Undercity, anything at all, bring it to me.
The spirits can guide you to anything you might seek within the Undercity, but only when presented with an offering. You will know such an offering when you find one.
Thank you again. Even if we fail, thank you.
